history.content: I swapped a course I'm enrolled with for CS61C, and now I'm on the waitlist for 61C, and still enrolled in the course.  Will the course automatically be dropped once I get off the waitlist for CS61C?  The total units I'm enrolled + waitlisted for (including the course I swapped with) is above the Phase I limit, but without the course I'm attempting to swap out of, I'm under the Phase I limit -- will the fact that I appear to be over the Phase I limit currently affect my enrollment?
history.subject: Question about swapping
